Start

If userType == 0 then
    Label: CustomerMenu

    Display list of 10 products (ID, Name, Price, Quantity)
    Display "Enter the ID of the product you want to buy:"
    Input productID

    Display "Enter the quantity of the product:"
    Input productQty

    If productID is invalid OR productQty is negative OR productQty > Quantity[productID]
        Display "Invalid input or insufficient stock"
        Go to CustomerMenu

    Add productID and productQty to the cart
    Reduce Quantity[productID] by productQty

    Label: CustomerOptions
    Display "Choose an option:"
    Display "0 - Proceed to basket"
    Display "1 - Buy more products"
    Display "2 - Return to main menu"
    Display "3 - Exit store"
    Input option

    Switch (option)
        Case 0:
            Display basket items with ID, Name, Price, Quantity
            Display "0 - Purchase"
            Display "1 - Continue shopping"
            Input purchaseOption

            If purchaseOption == 0 then
                Display receipt with all purchased items
                Display "0 - Exit"
                Display "1 - Go back to store"
                Input nextStep
                If nextStep == 0 then
                    End Program
                Else
                    Go to CustomerMenu
            Else
                Go to CustomerMenu

        Case 1:
            Go to CustomerMenu

        Case 2:
            Go back to main identity selection

        Case 3:
            End Program

End If
